title: Magnolia Bakery
info:
Info from Soundcloud:

Hey ppl,
Here I bring you a little chiptune track called 'Magnolia Bakery'.
I visited NY not long ago (which was a blast btw) and while I was there I went to the Magnolia bakery on Bleecker st. This track represents that good day.
It's dedicated to all the chiptune fans following my page (you're awesome) and when I was composing this I was in a pure a sugar rush state. Hope it's just as sweet as the cupcakes at Magnolia bakery!

/Zalza
